LongDescription: In Falcatan naval doctrine, heavy cruisers are meant to bear the brunt of the enmies firepower, while dishing out a heavy beating in exchange. They function as the anchor of a fleet, and when adequately supported by smaller vessels, they will inflict defeat upon any ship at any weight class. The Moccotar's are the epidimey of this doctrine. They sacrifice heavy point defense for outstanding forward firepower and excellent survivability. When paired with escorts to compensate for the poor PD, they will steamroll anything that stands in their way.
